docs.lead_paragraph: ALBANY, April 26 -- The State Health Department announced yesterday a new set of regulations for nurseries to protect newborn babies against infection. They will go into effect Sept. 1.
docs.abstract: Health Dept sets new rules for nurseries to protect newborn against infection, effective Sept 1
